data.description: This beautiful home sits on a large corner lot and is ready for its new owner! Located in a mature neighborhood, walking distance to Henry Elementary. The exterior has just been painted and new water heater installed! Gorgeous kitchen with an island, granite counters and stainless steel appliances. Walkout to the 10x12 deck and down to the large fenced in yard with a mature garden that showcases a variety of flowers, fruit and veggies! Three of the bedrooms are upstairs with an updated full bathroom. Enjoy the wood burning fireplace in the family room downstairs with built ins. This home also offers central air, to keep you comfortable year round. New garage doors just installed. Located close to military bases, restaurants and shopping!
